2. We use LoopA to leave behind the checked columns. Each iteration the matrix which we will check will decrease by 1 column.
this line will take care of that - ![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/07475203-3d6c-43b7-b4da-ffbdeda1a584_1658163863.0686345.png)

